VALUE OFFER: THE THOUGHT PROCESS
-----------------------
- convergent and divergent thinking
- math problem are convergent thinking (lots of variable and 1 single answer)
- you need to start thinking divergent (aka more solutions)
- think all possible uses of a brick
- how would you sell a brick

